    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Description\n\nBecause of the last changes, `oxlint` is not found in a monorepo, where each app has it's own `vite.config.ts`, but `oxlint` is installed only in the root project.\n```\n.\n├── apps/\n│   ├── app1/\n│   │   └── vite.config.ts\n│   └── app2/\n│       └── vite.config.ts\n├── node_modules/\n├── package.json\n└── vite.config.ts\n└── oxlint.config.ts\n```\n\nBecause the `root_dir` function looks for the first `vite.config.ts`, it finds it in for example `app1`, but the `node_modules` is not there.",
